        Update/replace escalation rules, which belong to a TrackerViewDto.
        Parameters:
        request - the request to replace the rules for the specified escalation group
        user - The user who replaces the rules for the specified escalation group
        tracker - is the tracker
        predicate - is the escalation group predicate
        escalationLevels - The new rules for this group. If null/empty it will effectively delete the rules of this group.
        Throws:

        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if validating the escalationLevels fails
